

**Matsh e doaj g pi himidkam **

1 Kush am waꞌi hebai amjed, tsh am dada g Peter g John wehm geꞌe cheopi t am. Kush d i waik ohla gam hu i juhk mo eda e aꞌahe mat wo e hoꞌigeꞌidahu. 2 Sh ab hema daha g shoꞌigkam hemajkam heg bahsho kolhai kihjeg mash hab e aꞌaga Si S‑kehg Kihjeg. Kush ihda oꞌodham ga hu e‑alijk amjed pi himdag. Kumsh wehs tashkaj am wabsh i bebhe ch ab dadsha ab kolhai kihjego. Kush wabsh haꞌichu ha tahni hegam mo am daiw. 

3 Tsh eda am wo i wahp idam Peter ch John. Sh ab haꞌichu chum ha tahni. 

4 Tsh ab si i nei idam Peter k hab kaij, “Ab g si i t‑neid.” 

5 Kutsh wa woho ab si i ha nei hab e ahgch mat wo haꞌichu mah. 

6 Sh oi wa hab wabsh kaij g Peter, “Neh, ni‑nawoj, pi ani ha lialiga ch wabshaba haꞌichu wo m‑mah mat heg baꞌich wo i m‑wehmt. K d ihda mant hab wo m‑ah mapt ab wo i hiw g Jesus Christ k wo kekiwua k wo hih.” 7 Bash kaij ch ab hahawa bei g nowij k ab i wuhshad. Kutsh am wa i hekaj ab gewpka g kakhioj. 8 Tsh am si uhgk daꞌa k kekiwua k am wa i hekaj s‑ap hih. Kutsh idam Peter im hu i wahp cheopi kolhai ch ed. Tsh heg ha wehm i wah k si chehk dadꞌehim ch ab si hehgchulid g Jiosh. 9-10 Kutsh si has i el g hemajkam am i neidok mo d hegai pi himidkam mo ab dahiwup kolhai kihjego. 

**Matsh am ha mihshmad g Peter geꞌe cheopi t am **

11 Batsh e juh ihda anai mash hab e aꞌaga Solomonbad Watto. Kush ihda pi himidkam gan hu wabsh i si e uꞌukch ab ha ab g Peter ch John mat pi wo i e gawulkai ab ha amjed. Tsh ab hahawa aꞌaijed i wohp g hemajkam k gan hu ha biha si has i elidk mat e doaj. 

12 Tsh am wabsh apꞌet g Peter mat am ha mihshmad k hab kaij: 

“Ni‑wehm oꞌodham, pi g am wo si e totodsid. Pi att g hejel t‑gewpkdagkaj doaj ihda oꞌodham, 13-16 Jiosh si Kehsha at hab t‑juni nach pi ab hiwig. K d hegai Jesus mam ahpim s‑muꞌamk ch ab mah g kownal Pilate. K eda g Jiosh d pionag g Jesus ch d hekia s‑apꞌekam ch pi ha chuꞌijig. T ha chum wo dagito g Pilate. M wabshaba ahpim hab ahg mat wo muꞌa k heg wo dagito mo d ha muꞌakam. K heg hekaj d em‑chuꞌijig mat e muhkid. K eda d hegai mo ab t‑makiog g pi ha huhugedam doakag. T wabshaba g Jiosh ab si haꞌichuchud k uhpam i wuhshad ab amjed g muhkig k am i bei dahm kahchim wui. Hegam t‑shohshonbad mash d Abraham ch Isaac ch Jacob ash ab si has i elid g Jiosh. Kum eda ab wui gegok g Jiosh si Kehsha. 

17 “Pegih, ni‑wepnag, mtp hems heg hekaj s‑muꞌam g Jesus mam pi mahch mo heg am d si Kehshaj g Jiosh mat wo t‑doꞌibia. 18 T eda heki hu waꞌi amjed an oꞌoha g kelibad Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam mat g si Kehshaj wo e shoꞌigch. T idani woho am hab e juh. 19 Pegih, oi g gam hu wo s‑ohhod g pi ap e‑chegitoi k ab wo i e nohnogi Jiosh wui. T heg wo s‑em‑hoꞌigeꞌid k gam hu hab wo i juh g pi ap em‑chuꞌijig k ab wo si i wechijid g em‑dodakag. 20 T ab em‑wui wo i hih g si Kehshaj Jesus. 21 K hab mahs mat an wo haꞌichugk ihda Jesus dahm kahchim ch ed am hugkam mat hab wo e juh hegai mo haschu i t‑tashogid g kekelibad Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam. 

22 “Neh, bash wa kaij g Mosesbad am t‑shohshon ha wui: 

Em‑kownalig Jiosh at ab wo hema i kei g haꞌichu i tashogiddam hab masma mat ahni am i ni‑kei. 

Kut ihda d wo em‑wepo oꞌodhamk. 

Wehs haꞌichu amt ab wo kaiha mat haschu ab wo i em‑ahgi. 

23 Kut wo e koꞌij matp hedai pi ab hu wo kaihamad. *Deuteronomy 18:15-19 * 

Neh, bash kaij g Mosesbad. 24 K wehsijj ahgachug g kekelibad Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam hegai mo haschu am hab i e junihim idani. Samuelbad ash d hema hegam. 25 Jiosh ash wa am ha ahgid g t‑shohshonbad matsh haschu hab wo t‑juni. K heg d ep t‑wuikam ahchim mach d ha amjedkam. 

“Bash kaij g Jiosh am wui g Abrahambad: 

Am ant wo hema i kei g m‑amjedkam mant heg hekaj ab wo i s‑ha hoꞌigeꞌel g wehs nahnko mahs hemajkam id dahm jewed. *Genesis 22:18 * 

26 “Neh, t wa woho hab e juh mat am i kei g e‑alidag Jesus. T heg wehpeg ab i s‑t‑hoꞌigeꞌel ahchim Tutuligo k ab t‑wui him k ab i t‑mah g apꞌedag matt ab wo i t‑nohnogi ab amjed g pi apꞌekam.” 

